text: La Quinta is a resort city in Riverside County, California, United States. It is in the Coachella Valley between Indian Wells and Indio. The population was 37,558 at the 2020 census. == References == == Other websites == * * The Desert Sun, Coachella Valley Newspaper * La Quinta Chamber of Commerce * Category:1982 establishments in California Category:Cities in California Category:Settlements in Riverside County, California
